summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the distribution and sale of meat, rabbit, poultry, and fish; amending Sections 3, 4, 7 and 30 of Ordinance 94465, as amended; amending Sections 9, 16 and 20 of Ordinance 80028, as amended; amending Section 3 of Ordinance 85679; to increase certain License and Permit Fees, provide for the depositing of License and Permit Fee receipts and assets of the Meat Inspection Fund into the City-County Health Fund, and abolish the Meat Inspection Fund, repealing Section 29 of Ordinance 94465, as amended, in connection therewith.
